This patch removes the definition for selectPtrAuthGlobalValue in the AArch64InstructionSelector class.
See issue: https://github.com/EESSI/software-layer/pull/1473#issuecomment-4302630567

Author: Aayush Joglekar (aayush.joglekar@surf.nl)

